column5: can anyone help me with info about the woman river chain near ear falls ontario? a friend of mine is going there and i would like to help him out with any info i can obtain. like best places for walleyes and trophy pike,and best action for small mouth bass. any info would be greatly appreciated.
i havent been there. but i have a friend who goes to woman lake camp every june and is more than pleased with walleye fishing and cabins. good luck
